  </div>

  <div class="projects">
      <div class="project-card">
        <%= image_tag "night-watch.png", alt: "NightWatch" %>
        <div class="project-card-infos">
          <h3>NightWatch</h3>
          <p>A social network where users can recommend movies to each other and create personal watchlists:
